data.description: Quiet country living conveniently located between Oxford and Holly Springs, yet close to Memphis.   This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath custom built home boasts hardwood floors & granite countertops. The open floor plan with vaulted ceilings invites views of sunsets,  a beautiful wooded 5.5 acre lot complete with  trails & space for outdoor fires. While the maple cabinets and surround sound system leave no doubt this country hamlet is an upscale delight. The 30x50 foot metal shop provides  ample space for parking and a work space.  Within 2 miles of Sardis Lake means you can be fishing in minutes.  Enjoy the peace of the country within earshot of the city!
